HEADWORD: bebeeru
<hw>be*bee"ru</hw> <pr>(b⟦esl⟧*b⟦emac⟧"r⟦udd⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>bibiru</asp>.]</altsp> <ety>[Native
